** lesson 1540 Philidor's Legacy
3.Nf7 checkmate! is a smothered mate identical to the one we saw in a
previous example. Are you beginning to see how tactical sequences are put
together? We know about the smothered mate and the mate with the queen on
f7. Then we add the new tactical device of the double check and now we have
a new idea, the queen sacrifice on g8 leading to smothered mate. 

